Zoolingo – Preschool Learning Games Privacy Policy
References in this Privacy Policy to “Mesh Soft Int. LLP.”, “we” “us” or “our” are references to Mesh Soft Int. LLP. The terms “you” and “your” are references to users of our app Zoolingo – Preschool Learning Games from time to time.
Mesh Soft Int. LLP. owns and operates the app and it also licences to third parties on certain terms the right to use certain proprietary web applications developed and owned by Mesh Soft Int. LLP. (Mesh Soft Int. LLP. Apps) via the Website, through Apple’s Appstore, through Google’s Playstore and/or through such other means as Mesh Soft Int. LLP. may from time to time determine.
Mesh Soft Int. LLP. is committed to protecting your privacy and maintaining the security of any personal information received from you. We take the privacy and security of your personal information seriously and will only use such information as set out in this Privacy Policy.
The purpose of this Privacy Policy is to explain to you what information we collect, how and why we collect it, and how we may use and disclose it.
Please note that our Privacy Policy may change from time to time and the new Privacy Policy will be published on the Website. By using the Website or any Mesh Soft Int. LLP. App and submitting your information to us, you agree to us using your information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
We invite you to also read our Terms and Conditions for more information on the use of the Website and Mesh Soft Int. LLP. Apps.
What does this Privacy Policy cover?
This Privacy Policy only applies to how Mesh Soft Int. LLP. deals with your information. It does not apply to any company outside the Mesh Soft Int. LLP. group or to any such company’s websites even if you access them through Mesh Soft Int. LLP., through the Website or through any Mesh Soft Int. LLP. App. If you disclose your information to any company outside the Mesh Soft Int. LLP. group, your information will be dealt with according to their privacy practices.
What information do we collect?
In a Mesh Soft Int. LLP. App we DO NOT ask you for personal information.
Where we receive personal information about you from other individuals, companies and organisations, we rely on these third parties to obtain your consent for us to use this information.
If you provide personal or other information to us you warrant the accuracy of such information and, where it is information about someone other than yourself, you warrant that you have that person’s consent to provide such information for the purposes specified.
In addition, when users visit our Website our server also collects non-personal server log data as described below in this Privacy Policy. We also use cookies as described below in this Privacy Policy.
Why do we collect your information?
We primarily collect different types of non-personal information about our users to fulfil their requirements for our services including Mesh Soft Int. LLP. Apps, to process orders, to carry out or respond to requests, to respond to their related enquiries or for any other purpose identified at the time the information is requested.
Use and/or disclosure of your information
How do we protect your information?
Mesh Soft Int. LLP. takes reasonable measures (physical, organisational and technological) to safeguard against unauthorised access to your information and to safely store your information.
However, you acknowledge that the internet is not a secure medium and the privacy of your communications and information can never be guaranteed.
Logs Files
When you visit the Website we automatically log your computer’s IP address, operating system and browser types and access times. We utilize this information to conduct site performance evaluations, to see where visitors are coming from and to keep track of clickstream data (that is, information about which screens our users visit on our site). Log files are not tied to personally identifiable information unless required by law. Users who do not register with us may browse the site without providing any personal information. These visits are also tracked for the purposes outlined above.
Cookies
Cookies are small text files that are often created when you visit a website or a web application. A cookie may be created when you visit us. We may from time to time use either or both permanent cookies and session cookies. The permanent cookie stores a random number on your device to help us count the number of times users return to our Website or Mesh Soft Int. LLP. App. The session cookie lets us know which pages within our Website or Mesh Soft Int. LLP. App you visit. Permanent cookies do not expire when you leave our Website or Mesh Soft Int. LLP. App and may be used on subsequent visits to the site. Session cookies expire when you leave this Website or Mesh Soft Int. LLP. App or switch off your device.
The cookie (whether permanent or session) does not contain any personal information about you, and it cannot be used to identify an individual user.
We use Google Analytics on the Website and on a web page presented in a browser view inside Mesh Soft Int. LLP. Apps. Inside Mesh Soft Int. LLP. Apps we use the restricted version of Flurry analytics.
You can set your browser not to accept cookies. You should read the information that came with your browser software to see how you can turn off the automatic download feature, should you so wish.
Children Policy
Our service is directed to children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect any personal information about children under the age of 13. If we obtain actual knowledge that we have collected personal information about a child under the age of 13, that information will be immediately deleted from our database.
If a parent believes that his or her child has submitted personal information to us, he or she can contact us via email. We will promptly delete the information upon learning.
If you have any questions or concerns, please feel free to contact us at: info @ zoolingo. com